OL,5,G0205 Emergency Helicopter Medics
OL,6,     FThe heli-medics help a teen
OL,7,     Fmotorcyclist who's been hit by a
OL,8,     Fcar and catapulted into the air. A
OL,9,     Fholiday fitness workout ends in
OL,10,     FCPR. And a lorry driver is trapped
OL,11,     Fin his cabin.
OL,12,G0305 999: On the Front Line
OL,13,     FParamedics treat a patient with an
OL,14,     Funusual stomach condition and a
OL,15,     F10-year-old girl who's having an
OL,16,     Fasthma attack and isn't responding
OL,17,     Fto her usual medication.
